Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:07.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A raid is a large-scale battle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with many adventurers, \Ninstead of the usual party of six.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The most common type is called a "Full Raid,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:19.40,Location,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Full Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and involves twenty-four players, \Nin four groups of six.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It comes with all the fun of a large-scale battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:28.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A raid requires more than high \Nlevels and good equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:32.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You must analyze the opponent and form a plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:36.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,and players must work together \Nto carry out that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:39.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't just a random group of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:43.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The most important element \Nis your willingness to trust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your companions with your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:47.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That means we'll need people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I know a place we could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.77,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.03,SignA,N,0000,0000,0000,,Susukino
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:27.25,HUD1,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(362,354)\an7}Susukino \N{\fs18}Japan Server \NSusukino \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:28.91,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The capital of the Ezzo Empire, and the \Ndefensive base against the giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.25,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fortress city of Susukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No guards, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They've gotten lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Things change in six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:43.53,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:46.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:54.61,Title,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1530,1)}The Outlaw and Mithril Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Outlaw and Mithril Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.61,HUD1,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(295,1)}Silver Sword Guild Hall \N{\fs18}Japan Server \NSusukino \NSeparate Zone/ No Monsters \NNo PVP \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.30,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's an unusual guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:14.38,HUD1,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(417,1)\an9}William Massachusetts \N{\fs20}Race/ Elf \NAssassin, Lv. 95 \NSilver Sword Guild Master
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, William Massachusetts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.15,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Call me William...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.86,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.95,Default - italics,W,0000,0000,0000,,Along with D.D.D. and the Black Sword Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.01,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Sword is one of Akihabara's big combat guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:32.19,Default - italics,W,0000,0000,0000,,When the Round Table was formed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.02,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they were asked to be one of \Nthe participating guilds, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:40.28,Default - flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Let those who care about the \Ncity solve its problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.15,Default - flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, we aren't interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.12,Default - flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Do it without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:52.00,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They moved their base here, to Susukino, \Nin search of more difficult raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:56.98,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that no one's \Npaying attention to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.50,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he's the only one I can ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've come with a request for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the Silver Sword guild master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.05,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:13.81,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,A man's come all the way out to the ends \Nof the North to ask for my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.31,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be rude to wait \Nto hear what he wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:20.99,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm requesting your participation in a full raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:27.75,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In a new raid zone at the lowest \Nlevel of the Depths of Palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:32.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a full raid, so only twenty-four \Nadventurers can go in at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We can't rely on numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.17,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll have to go in to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.39,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.03,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.43,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.40,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.33,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.26,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... There are monsters everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:57.18,Monsters,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(166,968)}Orks' Jelly\NRank/ Raid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The enemies are above level 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:00.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it will be extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.74,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,What types of enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The ones we saw were slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,More than five meters in diameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is only my guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:13.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,but given the layout of the facility \Nand the legends surrounding it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I believe there's a large monster, \Neither a giant or a phantom beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.46,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,A giant? Convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:22.23,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,We're based in Susukino, so we're used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.29,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,But there are still problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.55,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been to Susukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.12,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:35.73,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard it had gotten dangerous \Nafter the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:39.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Sword's presence here is a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like having a well-ordered \Ncombat guild around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.24,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't thugs like Brigandia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:50.24,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose those thugs must have \Nwandered off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:52.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:55.50,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:57.79,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.27,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Some members couldn't keep up with the raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.02,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,And some people are still in the guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they don't want to participate \Nin any more large-scale fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:08.76,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they've retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.71,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,They could do an easy raid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.76,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,but not a really rough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.10,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,This one will be top-level difficulty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:21.27,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,We're up to level 95, but we can \Nonly take twenty people at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is that because of your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.78,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that story about how if you \Ndie, you lose your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.99,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,We don't believe idle gossip like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.01,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't scared or anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.04,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you died since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Apocalypse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.92,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain it to someone \Nwho doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.77,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,When you die, you learn a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:55.43,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,That you suck, that you're petty, that you're lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.54,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,If you die a hundred times, \Nyou learn that a hundred times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.44,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,It gets too painful to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.70,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you had the guts \Nto show yourself again here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe the enchanter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.20,HUD1,D,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(417,1)}Demikas {\fs20}\NRace/ Human \NMonk, Lv. 93 \NBrigandia Guild Master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:24.28,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be that easy to find companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.13,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be up to Shiro's negotiating abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:29.09,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to find some backup candidates ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.25,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What criteria do you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Intuition, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.60,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's rather vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:38.28,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe "feeling" would be a better way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:44.50,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'll just slow you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.84,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You hold down the fort for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.35,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:52.45,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,This town is developing rapidly, \Nmaking it a worthy subject of study.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.49,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nice panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.30,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm forced to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.11,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You've got good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.63,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:05.21,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,But, though I'm not too familiar \Nwith adventurer customs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.46,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,aren't those what they call "hot pants"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:11.26,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Do they really merit the adoration given to panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:12.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you see them in your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.26,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,they're definitely pant—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.77,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.20,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Jerk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.02,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:30.43,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's Akatsuki's curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:34.31,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of phenomenon is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.75,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.46,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,They were just such beautiful curves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:49.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If a beautiful girl like me scratched her face up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.96,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be a loss to boys everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,She said it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.47,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's building yourself up a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you just get better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,My opinion of you keeps shooting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.76,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:04.98,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,She recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.23,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bright star, shining in the night sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:11.48,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the pretty-girl galactic idol, Tetra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.99,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Tetra"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.33,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tetra, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.74,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,but you're so self-satisfied, \NI don't want to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.83,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wink! Wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:25.50,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Taking into account a variety of factors...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Chief among them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.00,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,volume!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.75,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Marie is the clear winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.76,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:37.69,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.25,HUD1,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(421,1)\an9}Tetra \N\N{\fs20}Race/ Human \NCleric, Lv. 92 \NLight Indigo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.65,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,A level 92, like Shiro and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.77,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,So she's had combat experience \Nsince the Apocalypse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.57,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,She may actually work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, no matter how pretty I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,you're staring at me too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:02.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a girl like me puts out \Npheromones at all times, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Pheromones! Pheromones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:07.57,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,If they're coming from the butt you're sticking out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.00,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,maybe they're fart-o-mones, not pheromones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.25,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously awesome, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.94,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep hitting new highs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Idols don't fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:19.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This skeleton guy is harsh, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.29,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:25.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the guy in the armor \Nlooks easier to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:33.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I love rubbing against \Nguys as they freak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I hate it when \Nguys rub against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.50,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I said get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.95,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.31,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you absolutely sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.73,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a break in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:07.10,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That calm, arrogant attitude of \Nyours hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.39,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten my name, have you, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Mr. Democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.57,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Step outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.10,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You know what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.28,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Demi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.20,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,He's my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.96,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.13,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,He's my—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.21,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,You lost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.27,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,You lost, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.16,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pick a fight over it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.17,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.68,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you again, Demikas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:49.18,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat Shiroe anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:53.19,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten some raid items since our last fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:56.57,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you think equipment will \Nhelp you beat him that you can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you like more? \NHamburg steak or minced cutlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I like them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,With lots of that demi-whatsits sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:10.55,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rip you apart, just like you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't very nice, Mr. Deluxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.15,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You're deliberately screwing it up, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go, Mr. Tofu in Miso Sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.02,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You little—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:25.01,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Brigandia lost half its members.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can see why, after he lost
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to a cat swordsman who wasn't even in a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:34.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,His strategist, Londark, gave up \Non him and headed west, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what happened to Demikas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:40.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Demi-Demi and his whole guild \Nwork for Silver Sword now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:44.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how peace came back to Susukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:50.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And Demi-Demi's wife is so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.71,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,His wife?! For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's married? How enviable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's a noble with the People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.13,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He kidnapped her to make her his servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:02.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but supposedly, he's totally in love with her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:07.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's great cook, and Demi-Demi loves \Nher Hamburg steak and minced cutlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:08.78,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.39,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:16.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,So he's gained quite a bit of pudge lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:16.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demi-Demi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.75,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped at the last second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken a lot harder ones than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.50,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Just try saying that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:45.76,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll jam a slime down your throat and \Nfeed you to a giant, you bitch Tetra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.97,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Demi got mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I said get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I found her lying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.05,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:57.77,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,If you add that healer and Demi, \Nthat makes twenty-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.14,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to fight something that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:03.09,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,you can settle your differences with Shiroe in a raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.28,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.28,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
