Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.99,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,He's in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what I'd call working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:03.67,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run too far ahead on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.46,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are just slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Musclehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.51,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't put up a fuss about \Ncoming with us, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I knew William would be the commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:16.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't think we'd be walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be a flying idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.02,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone has a griffon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:27.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And I think William has some kind of plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:31.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We want to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the new members' personalities and \Nhabits before we get there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:39.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But first, are we even functioning as a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I'll ride Naotsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use me as a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:54.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a tsundere. You know you love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:59.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a beautiful idol. What if my feet get callused?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.42,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world would be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The sun wouldn't rise for three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.21,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then turn yourself into a snowman \Nand roll everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.84,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you good at getting stuck in snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is so easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's a warrior's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.76,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.13,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.55,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really aren't worried, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're just happy-go-lucky. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.34,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he hasn't changed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:35.57,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,But he came to the raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:36.85,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.55,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,The other idiots and I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:44.37,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,And if he can't, he simply isn't that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.59,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.61,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to rip things apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can finish it up this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:54.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:59.37,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,There are all kinds of events around New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:04.37,SignB,N,0000,0000,0000,,26 Days Until Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:02.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're having a rough time, Naotsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.76,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.32,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That was the guy who was chasing Serara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.68,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That demi-glace guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.13,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's Demikas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:16.69,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, William has an eye on him, so he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.80,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And his People of the Land wife \Nhas him on a leash, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.18,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.76,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,How about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating nutritious stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.16,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You want chicken, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:33.22,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's crispy outside, and juicy inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:35.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,In winter, chicken is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:38.12,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure pushing chicken hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Only twenty-six days until Christmas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.66,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:47.41,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope you can get back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.67,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:52.70,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:54.86,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, talk to you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.68,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.48,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Having a cozy telepathy chat at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.18,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you supposed to be a drama heroine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:11.19,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eventually going to say, \N"Which is more important? Me or your work?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.85,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Your imagination's a bit too active.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:19.68,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know where the \NSouthern spies might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.50,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we put strict rules in place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for talking with Shiroe and \Nthe others via telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.04,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.59,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the two of us decided to only \Ntalk once a day, at 9:00 at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.07,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:37.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say "Huh?" twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.32,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're only discussing basic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.87,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know where Naotsugu is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,So you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.96,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They're about to start a raid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.54,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.76,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they won't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They won't die, but they need a break, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.09,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to get in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:19:00.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's also my job to be the liaison between \Nthe Crescent Moon Alliance and them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:03.62,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's work... Work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:07.44,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Liaison, huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:09.12,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:12.38,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Marie, you're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:15.13,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm full, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.13,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You just ate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.89,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I feel so defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.40,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here in Akihabara, Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:42.49,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I need to ask a favor that only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.77,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to protect Princess Lenessia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:53.71,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,There are Southern spies in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.89,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,The princess might be in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.21,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,so I am to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.18,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.22,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:05.22,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I think his real goal is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.42,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.89,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:11.98,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A red bean bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.58,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Red bean bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:16.48,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what are you drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Roasted green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.49,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Apple tea isn't to your taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.74,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows red bean buns \Nare best with roasted green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.93,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.25,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:36.91,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I came to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:39.51,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,But there are still so many \Nthings I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:43.03,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,How adventurers think, their customs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:47.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my personal taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with apple tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:54.02,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:58.02,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hard job...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.41,SignC,A,0000,0000,0000,,Amenoma
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.29,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:26.21,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Powerful phantasm-level items can \Nonly be acquired through raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:28.30,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Like my lord's griffon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.05,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,They're proof that you've survived a \Ndifficult battle with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:36.80,SignD,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(334,1)}Dew Blade - Byakumamaru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.31,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done a raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:36.80,Location,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ringing Blade - Haganemushi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:41.38,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,So the only weapons I can get for \Nthis class are those that I can buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:42.66,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:49.33,HUD1,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1)\an9}Tadara \N{\fs20}Race/ Dwarf \NSamurai, Lv. 90 \NAmenoma
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:47.33,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Just so we're clear, I don't haggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:49.33,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.08,dewblade1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dew Blade - Byakumamaru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:54.08,dewblade2,,0000,0000,0000,,Effect/ Dew Blade - Byakumamaru\N{\fs16}AoE, Cold Damage \N\N{\fs18}Legend/ Dew Blade - Byakumamaru\N{\fs16}The favorite sword of Rugrius, the hero of Ezzo \Nwho drove the giants to the Jade Garden. \NThis blade freezes everything, and contains the \Nrage of the hero who met his death at the betrayal \Nof the Daughter of Elm, Sutu Inaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.08,dewblade3,,0000,0000,0000,,Price/ Dew Blade - Byakumamaru\N{\fs16}118,000 gold\N{\c&H2C18E1&}Not Enough Gold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.08,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's twice the value of everything I own!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.72,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:09.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the lowest level of the Depths of Palm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.97,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea there was a zone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This door really doesn't need to be that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:16.68,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,It's in here, right, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:18.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:21.46,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:25.99,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're after, \Nbut I won't let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.48,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rip apart all your wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:35.65,Default - italics,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change that stupid smirk of yours into a sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:08.48,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,In the lowest level
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Depths of Palm lies the \Nraid zone, the Abyssal Shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:13.70,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,There, the full raid finally begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:15.68,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,As the fierce battle rages,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, William, and Demikas fight with \Ntheir own thoughts in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:23.78,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,And in distant Akihabara, Akatsuki is uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.27,0:24:26.25,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Path to the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.27,0:24:30.94,Title,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,The Path to the Abyss
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.80,0:24:28.77,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Rise up once more.
